Dialogue: 5,0:00:01.48,0:00:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to muster the last of\Nyour strength, use it to leave here.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.82,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:07.98,0:00:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human who loses this much blood is gonna die!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in getting out if she's dead?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rachel Gardner is still alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.58,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get out right now, you can save her.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.13,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, and you will see.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go quickly, Zack!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to go!
