Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.36,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zack...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.34,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zack!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have guessed that it would end this way?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit that I was self-serving.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. Even though I was working for you...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... Nothing I did was wrong!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did for my own happiness,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and to stop anyone who\Nviolated the rules of this building,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,should have been beneficial to you, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.09,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that I got to see something\Nof profound interest, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.32,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed Zack was a being\Nthat possessed invisible wings,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.70,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but now those wings have become\Nentirely imperceptible to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Invisible wings?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you actually think he was an angel?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.05,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely because he was so pure that he\Nthought of only one thing: killing people.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.04,0:03:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Zack learned to wield his\Nblade for someone else's benefit.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.54,0:03:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of this, his blade broke,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and he fell from the ranks of angels, becoming a human.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, perhaps it is more accurate\Nto say he was always human.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.97,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, the one who showed this to me
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.15,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,was Rachel Gardner, the one I had denounced as a witch.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a transformation both dizzying and striking,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.32,0:04:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for a girl who was once so\Nself-serving and rife with contradiction.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.30,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back now, I see that the one who tried\Nto take Zack's humanity from him was me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why... why did you shoot me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my own vain attempt\Nat atoning for what I've done.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.59,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My observation and experimentation are over now,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as is my duty to stand in the position of God.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this, what are you..
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.46,0:04:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought that girl to this place,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.66,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but although you were meant to steal\Nher soul, you sought to give her one.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.22,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to become her God, did you not?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Danny, you are no God.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have known that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I hadn't done that, I'd have nothing!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first looked into Rachel's eyes,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.67,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they were the eyes of someone who'd lost all hope...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...and would never love anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.88,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give my love to those eyes for eternity.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave new meaning...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the life I thought I had lost!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That gave me the power to do anything!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't love her eyes any longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If she isn't all alone anymore,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.66,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no one left who'll accept the ugly thing that I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.69,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,By continuing to offer her your love, then,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you hoped that she would one day love you in return.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.02,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Danny, both you and I are mere humans, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... human?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.44,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There was never anyone here who wasn't human.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.47,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is humans who create God,\Nas well as angels and people.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.62,0:06:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That may have been true for Rachel Gardner, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.63,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ones who attack and destroy all that...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.80,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...are those same people.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.82,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you seen in the people you've known here?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.72,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, very little has significantly changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They were ugly, blind in their devotion, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...so beautiful.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.68,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Danny, I feel the same is true of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.81,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been here longer than any other,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I didn't realize it until now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already the end for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.19,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing you say I'm beautiful\Ndoesn't help much now, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.64,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there. We're almost outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you die on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. We're outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said I could save you once we got out.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up! Come on, Ray!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ray!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.28,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That priest... This is what he meant by saving her?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! Release the girl!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother resisting!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.20,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the girl, put your hands behind\Nyour head, and get on your knees!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.93,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ray, don't forget. I promised you...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I would kill you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl recovered from the burning building
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.32,0:10:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was found to be Rachel Gardner,\Nthe daughter of the murdered Mr. and Mrs. Gardner,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.00,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who went missing while their case was being investigated.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isaac Foster, the man arrested on\Nsuspicion of blowing up the building,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.25,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is believed to be behind several past crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Has Isaac Foster confessed?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not the one who blew up the building.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.99,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's also denied kidnapping the girl who was with him
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.35,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as killing her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Has he also denied involvement in other crimes?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.18,0:10:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, he admitted guilt to those with shocking honesty.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I don't lie," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Are you sure you can believe him?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Personally, I don't think he's lying.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.14,0:11:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.50,0:11:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, that's a dumb idea. Forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.79,0:11:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a twisted killer. No doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Have you found out how he's connected to the girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only answer he gives us about her is, "I don't know."
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.23,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, he actually asked us about her.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He asked if she was alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.65,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we told him she was, but all he said was, "Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}What was your first impression of Rachel Gardner?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought she was a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her expression was very desolate, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I can't blame her for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:58.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Has she told you anything pertaining to this case?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I've asked, but she denies knowledge of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}What sort of counseling are you giving her?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.17,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My top priority is to help her regain her peace of mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.36,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She gives very little in the way of facial cues,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.26,0:12:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she seems incapable of expressing her emotions.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.37,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... all she wants to know about is that murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}Could it be that she can't get the murderer out of her mind?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do think that's the case.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.24,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I've made an effort to keep\Nall information about him away from her.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've cut her off from the things that she fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:38.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i0\bord0\shad3.75\fs67.5\fnStreet Corner\4a&H00&\pos(960,855)}I hope she'll make a speedy recovery.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll keep working with her emotions,\Npatiently and persistently.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Rachel.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your counseling for today will be in the evening.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gorgeous day.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After breakfast, why don't we take a nice walk outside?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.94,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Places like this are so relaxing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.24,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.27,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rachel, could you wait here for a moment?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.58,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The suspect in these serial murders and kidnappings,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isaac Foster...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anything made you feel uneasy?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then have you been sleeping well?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.63,0:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry we started so late.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.64,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My session with another patient ran long.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll walk you to your room.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go by myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.55,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My, the sky looks so pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful night.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful night?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.23,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing to do on a night\Nlike this is get into bed and sleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.63,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rachel, could it be that you're afraid?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten much better since you came here.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing like who you were
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.78,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,when you kept asking about\Nthat murderer you were with.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.57,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So... to put you at ease, I'll tell you this.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That murderer...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.42,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...was sentenced to death.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He... was?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sure you're surprised,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believe this will help you sleep in peace.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.21,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.44,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight to bed and sleep, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.35,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth was that I hadn't slept well the whole time.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just couldn't calm myself down.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was sure I wouldn't sleep that night, either.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.56,0:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... there was nothing left to do but close my eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.31,0:18:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that boring look on your face again.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zack... How...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How what?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, weren't you in prison?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well... obviously, I left.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.79,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.88,0:19:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'd carry our promise with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.79,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you could go and take it for yourself, anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.80,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You still... want to kill me?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.48,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me.\NWhen I want something, I don't let it get away.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So hurry up.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you already forget?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.99,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Zack. I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never forget!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we promised!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.94,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I promised each other!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! So come on, Ray!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zack...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...kill me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.38,0:20:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, stop crying and smile.
